EN: The police arrested several suspects after searching his residence.

ZH: 那个逃犯在逃亡多年后被逮捕了。
EN: The fugitive was apprehended after years of being on the run.

ZH: 警方逮捕了一批涉嫌偷窃的小偷。
EN: The police arrested a group of thieves suspected of burglary.

ZH: 他们计划逮捕那个潜逃的罪犯。
EN: They plan to apprehend the fugitive criminal.

